#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:29
msgid "Hotkey"
msgstr "热键"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:31
msgid ""
"The axis of movement can be changed at any time during transformation by "
"typing :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y`, :kbd:`Z`."
msgstr "通过键入 :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y`, :kbd:`Z` 可以在变换过程中随时更改运动轴。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:35
msgid "Pointing"
msgstr "Pointing 指针"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:39
msgid "Axis-Constraint in action."
msgstr "轴约束。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:41
msgid ""
"Holding :kbd:`MMB` after starting a transformation lets you select an axis "
"to constrain to. A visual option to constrain the translation will be "
"available, showing the three axes in the 3D View space. A dotted white line "
"is used as a pointer. The axis of choice to confirm the operation will "
"depend on the highlighted axis about which the :kbd:`MMB` is released."
msgstr ""
"按下 :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y`, :kbd:`Z` 后， 再按住 :kbd:`MMB`  之后可以让你选择一"
"个轴来约束变换。约束变换的视觉选项将可用，在3D视图空间中显示三个轴。虚的白线"
"被用作指针。确定操作的轴将取决于 :kbd:`MMB` 释放时的高亮轴。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:47
msgid ""
"When you already moved the mouse in the desired direction, pressing :kbd:"
"`MMB` will lock to the axis which was pointed at."
msgstr "当你已经将鼠标移动到所需的方向时，按 :kbd:`MMB` 将锁定到所指向的轴。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:52
msgid "Axis Locking Types"
msgstr "轴向锁定类型"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:57
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:73
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst
msgid "Mode:     Object and Edit Modes (translate, rotate, scale, extrude)"
msgstr "模式：物体和编辑模式（平移，旋转，缩放，拉伸）"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst
msgid ""
"Hotkey:   :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y`, :kbd:`Z` or :kbd:`MMB` after moving the mouse "
"in the desired direction."
msgstr ""
"热键：    :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y`, :kbd:`Z` 或 :kbd:`MMB` 后，在所需的方向移动鼠"
"标 。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:63
msgid ""
"Axis locking limits the transformation to a single axis (or forbids "
"transformations along two axes). An object, face, vertex or other selectable "
"item will only be able to move, scale or rotate in a single dimension."
msgstr ""
"轴向锁定将变换约束到单个轴（或禁止沿两个轴变换）。物体，面，顶点或其它可选项"
"目只能在一个维度上移动，缩放或旋转。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:71
msgid "Plane Locking"
msgstr "平面锁定"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst
msgid "Mode:     Object and Edit Modes (translate, scale)"
msgstr "模式：物体和编辑模式（平移，缩放）"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst
msgid ""
"Hotkey:   :kbd:`Shift-X`, :kbd:`Shift-Y`, :kbd:`Shift-Z` or :kbd:`Shift-MMB` "
"after moving the mouse in the desired direction."
msgstr ""
"热键：   :kbd:`Shift-X`, :kbd:`Shift-Y`, :kbd:`Shift-Z` 或 :kbd:`Shift-MMB` "
"后将鼠标移动到所需的方向。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:84
msgid "Plane locking."
msgstr "平面锁定。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:86
msgid ""
"Plane locking locks the transformation to *two* axes (or forbids "
"transformations along one axis), thus creating a plane in which the element "
"can be moved or scaled freely. Plane locking only affects translation and "
"scaling."
msgstr ""
"平面锁定将变换锁定到 *两个* 轴向（或禁止沿一个轴的变换），从而创建一个平面，"
"元素可以自由移动或缩放。平面锁定仅影响平移和缩放。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:91
msgid ""
"Note that for rotation, both axis and plane locking have the same effect "
"because a rotation is always constrained around one axis. *Trackball* type "
"rotations :kbd:`R R` cannot be locked at all."
msgstr ""
"请注意，对于旋转，轴和平面锁定具有相同的效果，因为旋转始终受限于一个轴。 *轨"
"迹球* 类型旋转 :kbd:`R R` 则根本无法锁定。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:97
msgid "Axis Locking Modes"
msgstr "轴向锁定模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:102
msgid "Axis locking modes."
msgstr "轴向锁定模式。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:104
msgid ""
"A and B show Z axis locking in *Global* and *Normal* orientations "
"respectively. C and D show the same situation with face selection, E and F "
"with edge selection and G and H with vertex selection."
msgstr ""
"A和B分别显示Z轴锁定 *全局* 和 *法线* 方向。 C和D显示面选择相同的情况，E和F边"
"选择的情况以及具有顶点选择的G和H."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:108
msgid ""
"A single key press constrains movement to the corresponding *Global* axis. A "
"second key press of the *same* key constrains movement to the current "
"transform orientation selection (except if it is set to *Global*, in which "
"case the *Local* orientation is used). Finally, a third key press of the "
"same key removes constraints."
msgstr ""
"第一次按键约束运动到相应的 *全局* 轴。第二次按下 *相同* 键可将运动约束到当前"
"选择的变换方向（除非它设置为 *全局*，在这种情况下应使用 *自身* 方向）。最后，"
"第三次按同一个键将删除约束条件。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:113
msgid ""
"The orientation can be set in the :doc:`Transform Orientation </"
"editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/orientations>` selector of "
"the 3D View header."
msgstr ""
"可以在3D视图标题栏的 :doc:`变换方向参照坐标系 </editors/3dview/object/"
"editing/transform/control/orientations>`  选择器中设置方向。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:119
msgid ""
"For example, if the current transform orientation is set to *Normal*, "
"pressing :kbd:`G` to start translation, followed by :kbd:`Z` will lock "
"translation in the Z direction relative to the *Global* orientation, "
"pressing :kbd:`Z` again will lock translation to the Z axis relative to the "
"*Normal* orientation. Pressing :kbd:`Z` again will remove all constraints. "
"The current mode will be displayed in the left hand side of the *3D View "
"header*."
msgstr ""
"例如，如果当前变换方向设置为 *法线*，则按下 :kbd:`G` 开始平移，然后按 :kbd:"
"`Z` 将锁定在相对于 *全局* 方向的Z方向的平移，按下 :kbd:`Z` 将再次锁定在相对"
"于 *法线* 方向的Z轴。再次按下 :kbd:`Z` 将删除所有约束。当前模式将显示在 *3D视"
"图标题栏* 的左侧。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:126
msgid ""
"As can be seen in the *Axis locking modes* image, the direction of the "
"transform also takes into account the selection."
msgstr "从 *轴向锁定模式* 图像可以看出，变换的方向也考虑到了选择。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking.rst:129
msgid ""
"Note that using a locked axis does not prevent you from using the keyboard "
"to enter :doc:`numeric transformation </editors/3dview/object/editing/"
"transform/control/precision/numeric_input>` values."
msgstr ""
"请注意，使用锁定的轴不妨碍你使用键盘输入 :doc:`数字变换 </editors/3dview/"
"object/editing/transform/control/precision/numeric_input>`  值。"
